        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="s30" value="Notes&lt;br&gt;- Transaction raw schema is defined in data_generator/schemas.py and repeated in Spark StructType and Rust TransactionInput&lt;br&gt;- Rust TransactionOutput schema matches the final transformed transaction table&lt;br&gt;- Account schema is shared between generator, Spark ACCOUNT_SCHEMA, and Rust AccountInput/account_output_schema&lt;br&gt;- Spark accounts table is partitioned by country; Spark transaction table is partitioned by txn_year, txn_month, currency" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacing=6;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#666666;" vertex="1" parent="1">
